{
  "stem": "15577.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, they suffered mentally, maybe, the same way we suffered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we-- the Jews began to suffer, physically, quite quickly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly, but it was very short, after they occupied the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it-- it began with physical [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] beatings on the street, when they met Poles-- Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after a while, they began to-- it was a very well-known play by the Germans, when they met a religious Jew who has a-- a beard and-- and--",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Peyas-- so they cut them down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very spectacular for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made out of it very special spectacles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never had a beard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never had a peyas, so I was not exposed to this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But seeing the others, it was already-- I was already a part of this physical, let's say, torture-- or beginning of the physical torture.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This was the second part.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the third part began when they began to gather the Jewish people, in order to let them work on the streets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a [INAUDIBLE] word that means-- it was-- in the meantime, was already cold.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You have to know that in-- Cracow was conquered in September, and in late October or in the beginning of November, there's already snow in Poland.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the-- they gathered people to shuttle-- shuffle the snow, and which means-- not to shuffle away, to shuffle from one side of the street to the other, just in order to make the people work.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
